-- CANADA RESEARCH ROUNDUP-Enerplus Corp, Transforce, SNC-Lavalin 
-- 
-- Mon Jun 09, 2014 08:08AM EDT
-- None



June 9 (Reuters) - Securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several Canadian companies, including Enerplus Corp and Transforce, on Monday.

HIGHLIGHTS * Enerplus Corp <ERF.TO>: RBC cuts to sector perform from outperform rating * Transforce <TFI.TO>: Canaccord Genuity raises price target to C$31 from C$29 * SNC-Lavalin Group Inc <SNC.TO>: RBC raises target to C$60 from C$57; rating outperform  * Marquee Energy <MQL.V>: FirstEnergy Capital starts with an outperform ratingFollowing is a summary of research actions on Canadian companies reported by Reuters on Monday. Stock entries are in alphabetical order.  * Bellatrix Exploration Ltd <BXE.TO>: TD Securities cuts target to C$13 from C$13.50; buy  * Boyd Group Income Fund <BYD_u.TO>: LB Securities raises price target to C$50; rating buy  * Canadian Oil Sands Ltd <COS.TO>: Firstenergy Capital raises to outperform rating  * Capstone Mining Corp <CS.TO>: Canaccord Genuity cuts price target to c$3; rating buy  * Chinook Energy <CKE.TO>: Dundee starts with buy rating; price target C$2.75  * Enerplus Corp <ERF.TO>: RBC cuts to sector perform from outperform rating * Exchange Income Corp <EIF.TO>: LB Securities raises rating to top pick  * Just Energy Group Inc <JE.TO>: RBC cuts target to C$7 from C$8; rating sector perform  * Major Drilling Group International <MDI.TO>: CIBC cuts target price to C$8.50 from C$9.50 * Major Drilling Group International <MDI.TO>: Mackie Research cuts target to C$6; hold  * Marquee Energy <MQL.V>: FirstEnergy Capital starts with an outperform rating  * Regal Lifestyle Communities <RLC.TO>: Dundee raises target to C$8.75 from C$8.50; neutral  * Transforce <TFI.TO>: Canaccord Genuity raises price target to C$31 from C$29; rating buy * Sirius XM Canada Holdings Inc <XSR.TO>: RBC cuts target to C$9 from C$10;rating outperform